Nothing needs to be added to the .gitignore file based on the provided file changes, as they only include source code files (.blade.php) without any build artifacts, dependencies, or temporary files that would require ignoring.
```
# Compiled and build artifacts
*.pyc
__pycache__/
*.o
*.obj
dist/
build/
vendor/
*.class
*.exe
*.dll
*.so
*.a
*.out

# Dependencies
vendor/
node_modules/

# Logs and temp files
*.log
*.tmp
*.swp

# Environment
.env
.env.local
*.env.*

# Editors
.vscode/
.idea/

# OS generated files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Laravel specific
bootstrap/cache/
storage/logs/
storage/framework/
public/storage/

# Composer
composer.lock
```
# Compressed files
*.zip
*.gz
*.tar
*.tgz
*.bz2
*.xz
*.7z
*.rar
*.zst
*.lz4
*.lzh
*.cab
*.arj
*.rpm
*.deb
*.Z
*.lz
*.lzo
*.tar.gz
*.tar.bz2
*.tar.xz
*.tar.zst
```
